    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780330/extras/f93b980b15c46b2bc5aea5fce7ad4c03.poster.avif?t=1643928841\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780330/extras/f93b980b15c46b2bc5aea5fce7ad4c03.webm?t=1643928841\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780330/extras/f93b980b15c46b2bc5aea5fce7ad4c03.mp4?t=1643928841\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>召集你的派对</strong>并开始<strong>冒险</strong>到<strong>元素任务的边缘世界！</strong><br><br>独一无二的 <strong> 横向卷轴游戏 - 2D 中的 MMORPG </strong> 提供了 <strong> 开放世界 </strong> 充满生机、<strong> 社交、冒险<br>＆探索</strong>。<br>每一次探险都是不同的，每一个故事都是独一无二的，每一次体验都是独一无二的。<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 大型多人在线游戏<br><br></li><li> 2D 独特显示！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780330/extras/79bafe86cfdc0d9b37d77762f1ad8d20.poster.avif?t=1643928841\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780330/extras/79bafe86cfdc0d9b37d77762f1ad8d20.webm?t=1643928841\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780330/extras/79bafe86cfdc0d9b37d77762f1ad8d20.mp4?t=1643928841\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong> Roguelike 探险[/b​​] 3-5 名玩家，<strong>随机阶段</strong> 和 <strong>boss 打架！</strong><br><br></strong></li><li> 从 4 个不同的元素中选择一个独特的类：火、土、水和风！<br><br></li><li> 具有不同游戏元素（如商人和 NPC）的昼夜循环<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780330/extras/c18fa1cf97eee573a09ca46cbf052f60.poster.avif?t=1643928841\